{
  "texts": [
    "Information retrieval tools are responsible for analyzing repositories and collecting resources, which is pivotal in understanding the problem domain.",
    "We develop popular website search and documentation reading as information retrieval tools.",
    "Website Search Programmers often share solutions for various programming problems on websites where search engines consider them as knowledge resources.",
    "When encountering similar problems, developers only submit a question query to a search engine.",
    "The engine can provide useful programming suggestions."
  ]
}